snippet.title: Best VGM 1579 - Crystal Beans from Dungeon Explorer - Cursed Tree
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 982 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VfvadCcVXCo
Best VGM 2422 - https://youtu.be/jOTSv_JTC4w

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Crystal Beans from Dungeon Explorer (1995)
Cursed Tree
Yoshio Tsuru, Jun Takema, Tsukasa Masuko & Bang Heads
